Privacy Policy for Calixo -

Effective Date: 31/12/25

Calixo respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected, used, and protected when you use the Calixo mobile application.

1. About Calixo

Calixo is a multi-functional calculator app that provides various utility features including, but not limited to:

Unit Converter

Date Calculator

Finance Calculator

Compass

BMI Calculator

Shopping Calculator

Currency Converter

Random Number Generator

Equation Solver

Mathematical Tools

Fraction Calculator

Numeric Calculator

Calixo is designed for utility purposes only and does not require user registration.

2. Information We Collect

Calixo does not collect any personally identifiable information such as name, email address, phone number, or payment details.

However, we use Google Analytics to collect non-personal, anonymous usage data, which may include:

Device type and model

Operating system version

App usage behavior (screens visited, features used)

Crash logs and performance data

This data helps us improve app performance and user experience.

3. How We Use Information

The collected data is used only to:

Analyze app performance

Improve features and user experience

Fix bugs and crashes

We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties.

4. Google Analytics

Calixo uses Google Analytics for Firebase, which follows Google’s Privacy Policy.
Google may use collected data to improve its services.

You can review Google’s privacy policy here:
https://policies.google.com/privacy

5. In-App Purchases

Calixo does not contain any in-app purchases, subscriptions, or payment features.

6. Data Security

We value your trust and take reasonable measures to protect information collected through analytics services. Since Calixo does not store personal data, the risk to user privacy is minimal.

7. Children’s Privacy

Calixo is suitable for general audiences and does not knowingly collect data from children under 13. If you believe data has been collected unintentionally, please contact us.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated effective date.

9. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:

